name: close
description: Triggered when the SelfBot WebSocket connection closes.

name: error
description: Triggered when the SelfBot encounters a WebSocket error.

name: messageCreate
description: This event is triggered when the SelfBot receives MESSAGE_CREATE packet.

name: messageUpdate
description: This event is triggered when the SelfBot receives MESSAGE_UPDATE packet.

name: open
description: This event is triggered when the SelfBot's WebSocket connection opens.

name: raw
description: Triggered when the SelfBot receives any packet.
